title: (Mon Full) Bobby Celebrates His First Wedding Anniversary + Can Lunchbox Guess the Classic Country Artist?
itunes:title: (Mon Full) Bobby Celebrates His First Wedding Anniversary + Can Lunchbox Guess the Classic Country Artist?
description:
Bobby talks about what he did for his 1-year wedding anniversary over the weekend. We put Lunchbox’s music knowledge to the test. He tries to guess the classic country artists based on their most famous songs.
